(898, 0, 'Mompha Allegedly Arrested By INTERPOL In Abuja – Kemi Olunloyo', 'Trending', 'https://www.informationng.com/2019/10/mompha-allegedly-arrested-by-interpol-in-abuja-kemi-olunloyo.html', 'https://www.informationng.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/mompha-slams-hushpuppi-over-shade.jpg', 'According to popular controversial journalist, Kemi Olunloyo, businessman, Mompha, has been arrested in Abuja by the International Police (INTERPOL).\nMompha\nKemi Olunloyo revealed this online some moments ago as she revealed that she is still investigating on the cause of the arrested.\nAlso Read: Nigerian Businessman, Mompha Shows Off New Ferrari 488 Spider Worth Over N100 Million\nAccording to her, EFCC has declined to comment on the allegedly secret arrests.\nSee her post below:\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n View this post on Instagram\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n #BREAKING  Nigerian Bureau De Change King @mompha #Skyman reportedly ARRESTED in Abuja by the International Police @interpol_hq I have left several messages. Pls have patience. I&#39;m an investigative Journalist. Arrest was 3 days ago the same time he posted last a picture of his Lil girl. Interpol should release a statement soon on WHY he was arrested and exact whereabouts and whose custody he&#39;s in. The @officialefcc said they will get back to me too. Only good Journalists know about these secret arrests.They must be transparent though #humanrights #civilrights DETAILS LATER&#8230; #KemiOlunloyo  #kemitalkscrime\nA post shared by  Dr Kemi Olunloyo Pharm.D (@kemiolunloyo) on Oct 21, 2019 at 8:32am PDT\n\n\n\nThe post Mompha Allegedly Arrested By INTERPOL In Abuja &#8211; Kemi Olunloyo appeared first on Information Nigeria.\n', 0, 'Mon, 21 Oct 2019 19:26:50 +0000'),
